2. .dockerignore
Purpose: Keeps the junk out of the Docker Image. This makes your rag-app build faster and smaller.

Plaintext
# Don't copy the local database (it should be built fresh)
my_rag_db/

# Don't copy your local Mac virtual environment
.venv/
venv/

# Don't copy git history into the container
.git/
.gitignore

# Don't copy system files
.DS_Store

# Don't copy the README or diagrams into the running app
README.md
architecture.mmd
